Class User

Object
User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Applicant, HDBManager
public abstract class User extends Object
Abstract base class for all users in the HDB system. Provides common functionality for authentication and enquiry management.
Since:
2025-03-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
